{"tid":865181,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"為我而生係今季魔法戰爭既繼承人","createTime":"2018-10-16T21:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T10:47:25.000Z","uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"afdcab4c0c3b827dfaef8cf4da9add331a187a1c","tid":865181,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T21:57:20.000Z","msg":"第一集一開波青梅竹馬女主同就男主講自己有左<br />\n然後男主戴<span style=\"color: green;\">帽</span>個陣被魔法陣吸入左魔法世界<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/054955_64014aab6f5a30cf42f7dc5cd4b6f9da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F054955_64014aab6f5a30cf42f7dc5cd4b6f9da.png&h=28fddd15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後女主孕吐爆左隻怪出黎<br />\n男主有主角光環打撚死左隻怪<br />\n然後出到去無拿拿帶左去見國王<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/055245_10ea6ebc540aa34cffd86d2d71d616ce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F055245_10ea6ebc540aa34cffd86d2d71d616ce.png&h=a537e0ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國王話男主係被選中既人要求拯救世界<br />\n但係呢套野點可以如此兒戲<br />\n拯救世界既條件就係要同十二星座既巫女（其實係十三個）<span style=\"color: red;\">扑野</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n然後要生星之子出黎<br />\n因為頭先女主孕吐個陣已經流撚埋產<br />\n所以男女主扑野個陣入左ED<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/055649_e0fc1c230fbaa651ab3a50187e8df78f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F055649_e0fc1c230fbaa651ab3a50187e8df78f.png&h=c145c85a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a9735274c5153f980e3db8076bd699383faa553","tid":865181,"uid":35556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:17:40.000Z","msg":"痴撚柒線<br />\n好彩我見到監督係元永慶太郎就即刻熄左冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc647148a00f757183e03d9a54b60a9b240316bb","tid":865181,"uid":2002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2